summary: This is replacer for My fav women of Skyrim.
descriptionHtml:
[i][color=#ff00ff][size=2]     Hello guys :)[/size]
     This MOD is just replacer for My fav women from Skyrim.
     Meshes and Textures are standalone. CBBE and UNP body only.

     In the first version include [/color][color=#9900ff]Rikke[/color][color=#ff00ff], [/color][color=#9900ff]Carlotta [/color][color=#ff00ff]and [/color][color=#9900ff]Igdrod the younger[/color][color=#ff00ff].
     I hope you like it ;)

     18/04/2016 Added [/color][color=#9900ff]Gerdur[/color][color=#ff00ff], [/color][color=#9900ff]Olfina Grey Mane[/color][color=#ff00ff] and [/color][color=#9900ff]Sigrid[/color][color=#ff00ff] to v2.0 files.
     Fixed Rikke and Gerdur walking style.
[/color]
[color=#ff00ff]     18/05/2016 Added [/color][color=#9900ff]Camilla[/color][color=#ff00ff], [/color][color=#9900ff]Hulda[/color][color=#ff00ff], [/color][color=#9900ff]Narri[/color][color=#ff00ff] and [/color][color=#9900ff]Elisif[/color][color=#ff00ff].
     Fixed V1.0 and v2.0 face normalmaps and improved Sigrid's face(Little bit. So.....nvm!)[/color]

     [color=#ff0000][size=5]Important Notes[/size][/color]
[color=#ff0000][size=4]     This MOD is not support Wet and Cold MOD or something like that.
     If you use that, They will get hair clipping with Hood from that MOD.
     But Plz dont ask me support for that...... I dont. Sorry.[/size][/color]
